  "title": "Bank Wealth Executive/ Manager (Basic + Allowance + Performance Incentives + benefits)",
  "description": "<p>If you want to join the world of banking, to grow the wealth and enrich the lives of your customers, this will be the right opportunity for you.<br /></p><p>You will be the one supporting your customers in every step of their journey<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>You will be based in one of the bank branches in Singapore</li><li>Speak to the customers, able to provide good financial advice to the customers</li><li>Listen to the customers, recommend tailored financial solutions to the customers based on their requirements</li><li>Support the customers, helping your customers make better financial choices</li><li>Stay inform with market changes and latest industry trends</li><li>Cold calling, going out to meet customers and get more sales</li><li>Collaborate with the sales team and helping each other to succeed<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum local Diploma or Degree in related discipline</li><li>An interest in sales, able to attend to walk-in customers and do cold calling</li><li>No experience is required - Comprehensive training will be provided</li><li>Work as a team</li><li>Good interpersonal skills</li></ul><p><br />It's a 5.5 work week, working hours will depend on the bank branch opening hours.<br /><br />A rewarding career with good basic salary and attractive performance incentives.</p><p><br />Applicants who are interested to apply for this position can send your latest resume to alfred.lai@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg<br /></p><p>All are welcome to apply!</p><p><br />Alfred Lai</p><p>EA Reg No: R1545971</p><p>EA License No: 21C0434</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
